glishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "And I ask Him through you, and I present before you my needs, than you (all) be for me interceders, O my masters! For release of my neck from fire, and full for me my needs all of them, of the hereafter and the world, and suffice for me, my family, my children and the believing men and women from evil of all evil things from the Jinn and the human beings, small or big, then certainly I hope that I do not leave from your sanctuary. O my master! Blessings of Allah be upon you, except that my needs are answered, and that I take refuge to you in it, and I have hoped for His excellent help and blessings by your visitation, blessings of Allah be on you and upon the Imams from your forefathers, the Imams from your progeny, and mercy of Allah and His blessings.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WA AS-ALOHU BEKUM WA OQADDEMOKUM AMAAMA HAWAAA-EJEE FAKOONOO LEE SHOFA-A’AA-O YAA SAADATEE FEE FAKAAKE RAQABATEE MENAN NAARE WA AN YAQZEYA LEE BEKUM HAWAAA-EJEE KULLAHAA LILAAKHERATE WAD DUNYAA WA AN YAKFEYANEE WA AHLEE WA WULDEE WAL MOAMENEENA WAL MOAMENAATE SHARRA KULLE ZEE SHARRIN MENAL JINNE WAL INSE MIN SAGHEERIN AW KABEERIN FAQAD RAJAWTO AN LAA ANSAREFA MIN MASHHADEKA YAA MAWLAAYA SALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYKA ILLAA BE-QAZAAA-E HAWAAAEJEE WA MAA FAZE’TO ELAYKA FEEHE WA RAJAWTOHU MIN HUSNE MA-O’ONATEHI WA BARAKATEHI BE-ZEYAARATEKA SALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYHE WA A’LAL A-IMMATE MIN AABAAAEKA AL-AIMMATE MIN WULDEKA WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOH.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَسْاَلُهٗ بِكُمْ وَاُقَدِّمُكُمْ اَمَامَ حَوَآئِجِيْ فَكُوْنُوْا لِيْ شُفَعَآءُ يَا سَادَتِيْ فِيْ فَكَاكِ رَقَبَتِيْ مِنَ النَّارِ وَاَنْ يَقْضِيَ لِيْ بِكُمْ حَوَآئِجِيْ كُلَّهَا لِلْآخِرَةِ وَالدُّنْيَا وَاَنْ يَكْفِيَنِيْ وَاَهْلِيْ وَوُلْدِيْ وَالْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ شَرَّ كُلِّ ذِيْ شَرٍّ مِنَ الْجِنِّ وَالْاِنْسِ مِنْ صَغِيْرٍ اَوْ كَبِيْرٍ فَقَدْ رَجَوْتُ اَنْ لَا اَنْصَرِفَ مِنْ مَشْهَدِكَ۔ يَا مَوْلَايَ صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْكَ اِلَّا بِقَضَآءِ حَوَآئِجِيْ وَمَا فَزِعْتُ اِلَيْكَ فِيْهِ وَرَجَوْتُهٗ مِنْ حُسْنِ مَعُوْنَتِهٖ وَبَرَكَتِهٖ بِزِيَارَتِكَ صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْكَ وَعَلَى الْاَئِمَّةِ مِنْ آبَآئِكَ اَلْاَئِمَّةِ مِنْ وُلْدِكَ وَرَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "Ara